    "description": "<br><br>《Dimension Reign》是一款RPG游戏。玩家将通过分别组合两位主人公的技能，以及技能与攻击的联合来歼灭敌人。<br>通过破坏敌人的生命值槽来增加自己的行动次数，来封住敌人的行动，从而打倒在副本尽头等待的Boss。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >破防连锁攻击</h2>破防连锁攻击是这个游戏最独特的特点。玩家可以通过通过破坏敌人的生命槽（破防）来增加攻击次数。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1162480/extras/1ea6a9c484fbee8400a6b204a0eef6a5.poster.avif?t=1679686582\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1162480/extras/1ea6a9c484fbee8400a6b204a0eef6a5.webm?t=1679686582\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1162480/extras/1ea6a9c484fbee8400a6b204a0eef6a5.mp4?t=1679686582\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>另外，每次连锁攻击成功时，角色的攻击力都会提高，<br>从而造成超乎想象的伤害。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1162480/extras/079621674676067cf7443469fcf4e02c.poster.avif?t=1679686582\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1162480/extras/079621674676067cf7443469fcf4e02c.webm?t=1679686582\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1162480/extras/079621674676067cf7443469fcf4e02c.mp4?t=1679686582\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>*由于敌人会因为生命槽被破坏而晕眩，因此能完全封印敌人的行动。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >技能构建</h2>即使初看敌人的生命值非常高，玩家也可以通过装备效果，武器与技能的组合，对敌人造成压倒性的伤害<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1162480/extras/549d0a2b0accf085187f75fd91f172dc.poster.avif?t=1679686582\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1162480/extras/549d0a2b0accf085187f75fd91f172dc.webm?t=1679686582\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1162480/extras/549d0a2b0accf085187f75fd91f172dc.mp4?t=1679686582\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>寻找能够达到敌人的技能组合，请尝试各种组合来挑战副本。<br>您一定会迷上这个独特的战斗系统。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >角色强化</h2>角色等级提升后可以学习新技能，同时也能进一步加强技能的组合。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1162480/extras/56b195cadca5d185d330c439fd8055df.poster.avif?t=1679686582\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1162480/extras/56b195cadca5d185d330c439fd8055df.webm?t=1679686582\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1162480/extras/56b195cadca5d185d330c439fd8055df.mp4?t=1679686582\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >通关内容</h2>通关后获得的经验值能提升玩家角色的等级，从而收获新技能。<br>虽然已解锁的技能不一定会在每次的游戏中出现，<br>但为了让您能拥有更爽快的游戏体验，本游戏中设置了多种强大的技能等待您来发掘。",
